    "element_type": "p",
    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "Burdened with many cares, mothers sometimes feel that they cannot take time patiently to instruct their little ones and give them love and sympathy. But they should remember that if the children do not find in their parents and in their home that which will satisfy their desire for sympathy and companionship, they will look to other sources, where both mind and character may be endangered.<sup class=\"chapterendnote\"><a class=\"chapterendnote\">10<span class=\"chapterendnote\"><span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"MH 389.1\" data-link=\"135.1965\">The Ministry of Healing, 389</span>.</span></a></sup>",
