    "element_type": "p",
    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "Let parents devote the evenings to their families. Lay off care and perplexity with the labors of the day.<sup class=\"chapterendnote\"><a class=\"chapterendnote\">12<span class=\"chapterendnote\"><span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"CTBH 65.1\" data-link=\"14.314\">Christian Temperance and Bible Hygiene, 65</span>.</span></a></sup>",
