    "content": "Brought up under the wise and loving guidance of a true home, children will have no desire to wander away <span class=\"page-break\" data-page=\"194\"></span> in search of pleasure and companionship. Evil will not attract them. The spirit that prevails in the home will mold their characters; they will form habits and principles that will be a strong defense against temptation when they shall leave the home shelter and take their place in the world.<sup class=\"chapterendnote\"><a class=\"chapterendnote\">15<span class=\"chapterendnote\"><span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"MH 394.1\" data-link=\"135.1990\">The Ministry of Healing, 394</span>.</span></a></sup>",
